Scourge Stood near the base, his eyes focused on the doorway, he growled 
softly knowing someone was in there. He Knew maxima was there, but it was not 
right, it wasn't where he should be, The Wolf-Man bot crotched in the low brush, 
he'd flew in as a dragon following maxima, and now... now he waited, because 
even though no one else noticed it, a bot was walking around the base that 
normal eyes can't see... The wolf-bot watched the purple and yellow bot walk by.

--part1_1e2.b361dc2.2c1ea3ec_boundary
